[09:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Okay, so on my machine, it wasn\'t actually able to see the Pine and Cloud Code CLI. Uh so, I simply asked it to configure those for me, and it went ahead and configured everything. Which is pretty awesome.'

[09:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'But more interestingly, you actually see the same conversation happening exactly in the terminal where I started this. Right? So, these are different interfaces which are interacting with the exact same session.'

[10:04] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
